## Routing Architecture

```
app/
├── (main)/                         → main platform (header + footer)
│   ├── page.tsx                    → homepage
│   ├── courses/                    → program catalog + detail
│   ├── dashboard/                  → student/parent home
│   ├── portfolio/                  → portfolio builder UI
│   └── [role-specific routes]
├── (auth)/                         → login, register, role selection
├── (portfolio-site)/               → public student portfolio microsites
│   └── [username]/page.tsx         → rendered when subdomain is detected
└── middleware.ts                   → subdomain → route rewrite
```

